Package pacman.game

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Constants
    This class contains the enumerations for the moves and the ghosts as well as as the constants of the game.
    Game
    The implementation of Ms Pac-Man.
    GameView
    This class is the view that displays the game.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Constants.DM
    DM stands for Distance Metric, a simple enumeration for use with methods that require a distance metric.
    Constants.GHOST
    Enumeration for the ghosts.
    Constants.MOVE
    Enumeration for the moves that are possible in the game.
